      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MEPUNGA ZIRCON (7) comes off a big run when second in a useful 33.95 at this track over 595m. Should be in this for a long way. WEBLEC MEMPHIS (6) racing well without winning, placing at his last four runs. Last time finished 3rd on March 12 over 515m at this track behind Mepunga Express beaten 0.7 lengths (29.73) in a Grade 4/5. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Hard to beat again. UNLEASH THE LION (8) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (29.36) in a Grade 5 at Sale. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from five attempts. Cannot be underestimated. POINT BREAK (4) has strong credentials over this journey.",
